'''Francis''' (full name and dates of birth and death unknown) was an English [[cricket]]er who played for [[Hampshire county cricket teams]] organised by the [[Hambledon Club]]. Possibly related to [[Richard Francis]], he played in one first-class match against [[Kent county cricket teams|Kent]] in 1775.

