'''Omladinski košarkaški klub Dunav''' ({{lang-sr-cyr|Омладински кошаркашки клуб Дунав}}), commonly referred to as '''OKK Dunav''', is a men's professional [[basketball]] [[Sports club|club]] based in [[Stari Banovci]], [[Serbia]]. They are currently competing in the [[Basketball League of Serbia]].

