'''Panama Cricket Association''' is the official [[Sport governing body|governing body]] of the sport of [[cricket]] in [[Panama]]. Panama Cricket Association is Panama's representative at the [[International Cricket Council]] and is an affiliate member and has been a member of that body since 2002. It is included in the [[ICC Americas]] region.

