{{Infobox football tournament | name = Somalia Cup | logo = | region = Somalia | founded = 1977 | current champions = [[Elman FC]] (2017) | most successful club = [[Horseed FC]] (4) | website = | current = }}
The '''Somalia Cup''' is the top knockout [[association football|football]] tournament in Somalia. [[Horseed FC|Horseed]] are the competition's most successful club, having won it four times.<ref name=RSSSF>[http://www.rsssf.com/tabless/somacuphist.html Somalia Cup Winners] RSSSF</ref>
