'''Tout Puissant Union Sportive Centrafricaine de Bangui''' is an [[association football]] club from [[Central African Republic]] based in [[Bangui]].<ref>http://www.sportstats.com/soccer/central-african-republic/detail/tp-usca-bangui-z1w7OQx6/</ref>
